spec_data.Name: gnome-boxes
spec_data.Description:
gnome-boxes lets you easily create, setup, access, and use:
  * remote machines
  * remote virtual machines
  * local virtual machines
  * When technology permits, set up access for applications on
    local virtual machines

spec_data.Summary: A simple GNOME 3 application to access remote or virtual systems
